---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const post = {
  title: 'Role of Engineering in Developing Advanced Mining Systems',
  category: 'ENGINEERING',
  date: 'March 16, 2026',
  author: 'Michael Chen',
  authorRole: 'Chief Executive Officer',
  authorImage: '/images/team/member-1.jpg',
  image: '/images/blog/post-1.jpg',
  content: `
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      The mining industry has undergone a remarkable transformation over the past decade, driven largely by advances in engineering and technology. Today's mining operations bear little resemblance to those of even twenty years ago, with sophisticated systems and automated processes revolutionizing how we extract and process valuable resources.
    </p>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-4 mt-10">The Evolution of Mining Engineering</h2>
    
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Modern mining engineering encompasses a broad spectrum of disciplines, from geological surveying and resource estimation to equipment design and environmental management. The integration of digital technologies has created opportunities for unprecedented precision and efficiency in every aspect of the mining lifecycle.
    </p>
    
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      One of the most significant developments has been the implementation of real-time monitoring systems. These sophisticated networks of sensors and data analytics platforms allow engineers to track every aspect of mining operations, from equipment performance to environmental conditions, enabling rapid response to potential issues and optimization of production processes.
    </p>
    
    <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-[#F5A623] pl-6 py-2 my-8 bg-gray-50">
      <p class="text-[#1A1A1A] text-lg italic font-medium">
        "The future of mining lies not in extracting more resources, but in extracting them more intelligently, safely, and sustainably."
      </p>
    </blockquote>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-4 mt-10">Automation and Robotics</h2>
    
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      The deployment of autonomous vehicles and robotic systems represents one of the most visible changes in modern mining. These technologies not only improve safety by removing workers from hazardous environments but also enhance productivity through continuous operation and precise control.
    </p>
    
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Remote operation centers now allow skilled operators to control equipment from safe distances, while artificial intelligence systems optimize routes, predict maintenance needs, and manage complex logistics operations with minimal human intervention.
    </p>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-4 mt-10">Sustainable Engineering Solutions</h2>
    
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Environmental responsibility has become a central focus of mining engineering. Modern approaches prioritize minimal environmental impact, efficient resource utilization, and comprehensive rehabilitation programs. Engineers are developing innovative solutions for water management, waste reduction, and energy efficiency that are transforming the industry's environmental footprint.
    </p>
    
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      The integration of renewable energy sources, such as solar and wind power, into mining operations represents a significant shift toward sustainability. These technologies not only reduce carbon emissions but also provide operational advantages in remote locations where traditional power infrastructure may be unavailable.
    </p>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-4 mt-10">Looking Ahead</h2>
    
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      As we look to the future, the role of engineering in mining will only continue to expand. Emerging technologies such as artificial intelligence, machine learning, and advanced materials science promise to further revolutionize the industry. The challenge for mining engineers will be to harness these technologies while maintaining the highest standards of safety, environmental responsibility, and social license to operate.
    </p>
  `
};

const relatedPosts = [
  {
    title: 'Engineering Innovation Transforming Modern Mining Operations',
    image: '/images/blog/post-2.jpg',
    category: 'INNOVATION',
    date: 'March 15, 2026',
    slug: 'post-2',
  },
  {
    title: 'Mining Industry Supporting Modern Industrial Infrastructure',
    image: '/images/blog/post-3.jpg',
    category: 'INDUSTRY',
    date: 'March 14, 2026',
    slug: 'post-3',
  },
  {
    title: 'Sustainable Mining Practices Improving Resource Extraction',
    image: '/images/blog/post-5.jpg',
    category: 'SUSTAINABILITY',
    date: 'March 12, 2026',
    slug: 'post-5',
  },
];

const tags = ['Engineering', 'Technology', 'Automation', 'Innovation', 'Mining'];
---

<Layout title={`${post.title} | Minetra Blog`}>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[500px] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img 
        src={post.image}
        alt={post.title}
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 via-black/60 to-black/30"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10 text-white py-16">
      <nav class="mb-6">
        <ol class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-[#F5A623] transition">Home</a></li>
          <li class="text-gray-500">/</li>
          <li><a href="/blog" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-[#F5A623] transition">Blog</a></li>
          <li class="text-gray-500">/</li>
          <li><span class="text-[#F5A623]">{post.category}</span></li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <span class="inline-block bg-[#F5A623] text-white text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        {post.category}
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 max-w-4xl leading-tight">
        {post.title}
      </h1>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 text-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" x2="16" y1="2" y2="6"/><line x1="8" x2="8" y1="2" y2="6"/><line x1="3" x2="21" y1="10" y2="10"/></svg>
          <span>{post.date}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          <span>{post.author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Blog Content Section -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-8">
          <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <Fragment set:html={post.content} />
          </article>

          <!-- Tags -->
          <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-[#1A1A1A] font-semibold mr-2">Tags:</span>
              {tags.map(tag => (
                <a href="#" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-sm hover:bg-[#F5A623] hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                  {tag}
                </a>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Share -->
          <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-[#1A1A1A] font-semibold">Share:</span>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#3b5998] text-white flex items-center justify-center hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1da1f2] text-white flex items-center justify-center hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M22 4s-.7 2.1-2 3.4c1.6 10-9.4 17.3-18 11.6 2.2.1 4.4-.6 6-2C3 15.5.5 9.6 3 5c2.2 2.6 5.6 4.1 9 4-.9-4.2 4-6.6 7-3.8 1.1 0 3-1.2 3-1.2z"/></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#0077b5] text-white flex items-center justify-center hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect width="4" height="12" x="2" y="9"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-8">
          <!-- Author Card -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-6 pb-4 border-b border-gray-200">About Author</h3>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <img 
                src={post.authorImage}
                alt={post.author}
                class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full object-cover"
              />
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">{post.author}</h4>
                <p class="text-[#F5A623] text-sm">{post.authorRole}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Experienced professional with extensive knowledge in mining operations and industrial development.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Categories -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-6 pb-4 border-b border-gray-200">Categories</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center justify-between text-gray-600 hover:text-[#F5A623] transition-colors"><span>Engineering</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-400">(4)</span></a></li>
              <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center justify-between text-gray-600 hover:text-[#F5A623] transition-colors"><span>Innovation</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-400">(3)</span></a></li>
              <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center justify-between text-gray-600 hover:text-[#F5A623] transition-colors"><span>Industry</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-400">(3)</span></a></li>
              <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center justify-between text-gray-600 hover:text-[#F5A623] transition-colors"><span>Sustainability</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-400">(2)</span></a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Recent Posts -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-6 pb-4 border-b border-gray-200">Recent Posts</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              {relatedPosts.slice(0, 3).map(related => (
                <a href={`/blog/${related.slug}`} class="flex gap-4 group">
                  <img 
                    src={related.image}
                    alt={related.title}
                    class="w-20 h-20 object-cover flex-shrink-0"
                  />
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#1A1A1A] group-hover:text-[#F5A623] transition-colors line-clamp-2 leading-snug">
                      {related.title}
                    </h4>
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1 block">{related.date}</span>
                  </div>
                </a>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Posts Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-[2px] bg-[#F5A623]"></div>
          <span class="text-[#F5A623] text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[3px]">Related</span>
          <div class="w-8 h-[2px] bg-[#F5A623]"></div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">
          Related Articles
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        {relatedPosts.map(related => (
          <article class="bg-white border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-[16/10]">
              <img 
                src={related.image}
                alt={related.title}
                class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
              />
              <span class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-[#F5A623] text-white text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 uppercase tracking-wider">
                {related.category}
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-400 text-sm mb-3">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" x2="16" y1="2" y2="6"/><line x1="8" x2="8" y1="2" y2="6"/><line x1="3" x2="21" y1="10" y2="10"/></svg>
                <span>{related.date}</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-[#F5A623] transition-colors">
                {related.title}
              </h3>
            </div>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
